<br>
The news has been replete with talk of the increasing involvement of many governments of the world in the problems in the Middle East, particularly the ongoing terror war being waged by the PLO against Israel. <br>
<br>
We are told of a time that will come when ALL the nations of the world will be burdened by what will be happening, in the future, in Israel and in Jerusalem, in particular.  Zech 12:3<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>And in that day will I make Jerusalem a burdensome stone for all people: all that burden themselves with it shall be cut in pieces, though all the people of the earth be gathered together against it.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->  <br>
<br>
Any comments on the relationship between the present situation and 'that day'?<br>
<br>
Just wondering.<br>
<br>
God Bless you.  Charlie Baker.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsparrowshearth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jeffthefinn>jeffthefinn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://webpages.charter.net/nilus/finnbutton.GIF" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#B87333>(6/5/03 10:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsparrowshearthfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://webpages.charter.net/nilus/jfinn.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A Question.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>terror war being waged by the PLO against Israel<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
