<br>
They appear to have an affiliation with Islam and the God of Islam is Allah, not God the Almighty of the Bible. <br>
<br>
Why do you champion the PLO who teach their children to hate, brainwash them into becoming suicide bombers, honor them for killing women and children and pay handsome sums of money to their parents, when their children commit suicide by blowing themselves up, to the glory of Allah?<br>
<br>
Just wondering.<br>
